com.vmware.nsx

Class NsxFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.NsxFactory

  • public class NsxFactory
extends Object
    NsxFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
